============================================================
测试 1: JsonRpcError 错误渲染
============================================================

【输入】:
{
  "test_name": "test_main_renders_jsonrpc_error_as_structured_json",
  "description": "模拟 create_page 抛出 JsonRpcError",
  "argv": [
    "manage_content.py",
    "--create",
    "--slug",
    "dup",
    "--title",
    "Title"
  ],
  "mocked_function": "create_page",
  "raised_exception": {
    "type": "JsonRpcError",
    "code": -32001,
    "message": "Slug already exists",
    "data": {
      "slug": "dup"
    }
  }
}

【输出】:
{
  "exit_code": 1,
  "stdout": {
    "status": "error",
    "error_type": "jsonrpc",
    "code": -32001,
    "message": "Slug already exists",
    "data": {
      "slug": "dup"
    }
  }
}

【验证】: ✓ 通过

